metadata.name: Happy Holidays!
metadata.description:
My first open edition/FREE mint on Manifold!

This was one of the first photographs made in my project "A Dying Light" and is not going to be making it into the final book. This edition is open and the mint period will end on January 1st, 2023! This is the first piece available from "A Dying Light", which will be my first hard cover coffee table photo book! Thank you to everyone who supports me in this dream, I couldn't do it without all of you!
